  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> June 4, 2025</p>

  <p>This privacy policy explains how I, Milhim Milhim, handle any information that may be collected by my LinkedIn Developer App.</p>

  <p><strong>Information Collection and Use:</strong>  
  My application may collect basic public profile information such as your name, email address, and profile picture solely to provide the intended functionality. I do not sell, rent, or misuse this information in any way.</p>

  <p><strong>Data Sharing:</strong>  
  Any data collected through this application will not be shared with third parties, except as required by law or for security compliance.</p>

  <p><strong>Cookies and Tracking:</strong>  
  The application does not use cookies or any third-party tracking tools.</p>

  <p><strong>Data Security:</strong>  
  I use industry-standard security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.</p>

  <p><strong>Your Rights:</strong>  
  You have the right to access, update, or request deletion of your data at any time. To make such a request, please contact me directly using the email below.</p>

  <p><strong>Contact:</strong>  
  If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please feel free to reach out to me at <a href="mailto:milhim.a.milhim@gmail.com">milhim.a.milhim@gmail.com</a>.</p>

  <p>This policy may be updated occasionally. Please review it periodically for any changes.</p>
